## Page Templates

When building a new page, consult the reference in `docs/page-templates/`:

| Template | Use for |
|----------|---------|
| `dashboard.md` | List pages, overview pages with metrics |
| `detail.md` | Single-entity view with actions |
| `form.md` | Create and edit forms with validation |

Every page must handle: loading state, error state, empty state, and the not-found case.

