## Design System ({{ design_style }})

{% if styling == "tailwind" %}
Utility classes from Tailwind CSS. Use the `cn()` helper from `src/lib/utils.ts` to merge conditional classes.
{% elif styling == "css-modules" %}
CSS Modules. Each component has a `.module.css` sibling. Global tokens in `src/app/globals.css`.
{% elif styling == "scss" %}
SCSS Modules. Design tokens in `src/styles/_variables.scss`. Import per component.
{% endif %}

{% if ui_library == "shadcn-ui" %}
Components in `src/components/ui/` are shadcn/ui components - they are owned by this project. Customize them directly; do not fight the library.
{% elif ui_library == "radix-ui" %}
Radix UI primitives are used unstyled. All styling is applied via the project's CSS approach.
{% endif %}

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- Restrained color palette: neutrals + one accent
- Generous whitespace, strong typographic hierarchy
- No decorative elements - every visual element carries meaning
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Structured, data-dense layouts
- Professional blues/grays, clear hierarchy
- Always-visible labels on interactive elements
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Rounded corners, vibrant colors, micro-interactions
- Friendly copy tone, icon-forward navigation
- Animation on user-triggered actions only (not on page load)
{% endif %}
